{"_path":"/maps/_workflow/linter/linter","_dir":"linter","_draft":false,"_partial":true,"_locale":"","title":"代码规范","description":"代码质量检查工具与风格规范，涵盖 ESLint、Prettier 等工具的配置与最佳实践","body":{"type":"root","children":[{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"主题"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"主题"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_workflow/linter/eslint"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ESLint"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"/maps/_workflow/linter/code-style"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Code Style"}]},{"type":"text","value":" - 代码风格与格式规范"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"eslint-9x-flat-config"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ESLint 9.x Flat Config"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"如何迁移到-flat-config"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"如何迁移到 Flat Config？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://zh-hans.eslint.org/docs/latest/use/configure/migration-guide","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"配置迁移指南@eslint"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"为什么推荐使用-antfueslint-config"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为什么推荐使用 @antfu/eslint-config？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"@antfu/eslint-config 是 Anthony Fu 维护的一套现代化 ESLint 共享配置，专为 Flat Config 设计，集成了 TypeScript、Vue、React 等生态的最佳实践，开箱即用。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h2","props":{"id":"代码格式化策略"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"代码格式化策略"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"为什么-antfu-不使用-prettier"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为什么 antfu 不使用 Prettier？"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"Prettier 的自动换行策略使代码 diff 变得难以阅读，并且没有选项可以用来关闭 print-width 配置的换行策略。尽管可以通过 ESLint 来纠正 Prettier 的行为，但是这麻烦且降低了性能。所以 antfu 的策略是使用自己配置的整套 ESLint 规则共享包。"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"见："},{"type":"element","tag":"a","props":{"href":"https://antfu.me/posts/why-not-prettier-zh","rel":["nofollow"]},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"为什么我不使用 Prettier | antfu"}]}]},{"type":"element","tag":"h4","props":{"id":"eslint-only-方案的优势"},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"ESLint-only 方案的优势"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"p","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"使用纯 ESLint 进行代码格式化的优势包括："}]},{"type":"element","tag":"ul","props":{},"children":[{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"统一的配置入口，减少工具链复杂度"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"更好的性能（无需在 ESLint 和 Prettier 之间来回传递）"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"更灵活的规则定制能力"}]},{"type":"element","tag":"li","props":{},"children":[{"type":"text","value":"更好的编辑器集成体验"}]}]}],"toc":{"title":"","searchDepth":2,"depth":2,"links":[{"id":"主题","depth":2,"text":"主题"},{"id":"eslint-9x-flat-config","depth":2,"text":"ESLint 9.x Flat Config"},{"id":"代码格式化策略","depth":2,"text":"代码格式化策略"}]}},"_type":"markdown","_id":"content:6.maps:_workflow:linter:linter.md","_source":"content","_file":"6.maps/_workflow/linter/linter.md","_stem":"6.maps/_workflow/linter/linter","_extension":"md"}